## Salesman API

### Get Salesman

Returns salesman profile, assigned route, van store, and price phase.


GET /salesman/{salesmanCode}


#### Path Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| salesmanCode | string | ✅ | Salesman unique code |

#### Query Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| companyNumber | string | ✅ | Company identifier |

#### Response Fields

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| companyNumber | string | Company identifier |
| salesmanCode | string | Salesman unique code |
| salesmanNameAr | string | Salesman Arabic name |
| salesmanNameEn | string | Salesman English name |
| salesmanPhone | string | Contact number |
| routeCode | string | Assigned route code |
| routeNameAr | string | Route Arabic name |
| routeNameEn | string | Route English name |
| storeNumber | string | Assigned van / warehouse number |
| pricePhase | string | Default price phase (1–4) |
| isActive | boolean | Salesman active status |

#### Example Request


GET /salesman/S012?companyNumber=C001


#### Example Response

json
{
  "companyNumber": "C001",
  "salesmanCode": "S012",
  "salesmanNameAr": "أحمد المصري",
  "salesmanNameEn": "Ahmad Al-Masri",
  "salesmanPhone": "0791234567",
  "routeCode": "R-A01",
  "routeNameAr": "مسار وسط عمان",
  "routeNameEn": "Central Amman Route",
  "storeNumber": "4",
  "pricePhase": "2",
  "isActive": true
}


