## Item API

### Get Item

Returns full item details including units and price phases.


GET /items/{itemCode}


#### Path Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| itemCode | string | ✅ | Unique item code |

#### Query Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| companyNumber | string | ✅ | Company identifier |
| salesmanCode | string | ✅ | Salesman identifier |

#### Response Fields

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| companyNumber | string | Company identifier |
| salesmanCode | string | Salesman identifier |
| itemCode | string | Unique item identifier |
| itemNameAr | string | Arabic item name |
| itemNameEn | string | English item name |
| itemPrice | decimal(3) | Base unit price |
| itemBarcode | string | Item barcode number |
| itemPic | string | Image URL |
| itemCategory | string | Category name |
| taxPerc | decimal | Tax percentage |
| itemUnits | array | List of available units — see below |
| itemPriceList | array | Tiered price phases — see below |

#### itemUnits Fields

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| unitName | string | Unit label (piece, carton, pallet…) |
| unitCode | string | Unit identifier code |
