| unitQty | integer | Available stock qty for this unit |

#### itemPriceList Fields

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| phaseNumber | string | Phase index (1, 2, 3, 4) |
| phasePrice | decimal(3) | Price for this phase |

