## Item Balance API

### Get Item Balance

Returns stock balance for an item across stores or for a specific store.


GET /itemBalance


#### Query Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Required | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| companyNumber | string | ✅ | Company identifier |
| salesmanCode | string | ✅ | Salesman identifier |
| itemNumber | string | ✅ | Item number to query |
| storeNo | string | ❌ | Filter by store number. Omit to return all stores |

#### Response

Returns an *array*. Always an array even when filtering by a single store.

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| companyNumber | string | Company identifier |
| salesmanCode | string | Salesman identifier |
| itemNumber | string | Item reference number |
| itemQty | integer | Available quantity in this store |
| storeNumber | string | Store / warehouse identifier |

#### Store Numbers Reference

| storeNumber | Arabic | English |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | مخزن رئيسي | Main Warehouse |
| 2 | مخزن B | Warehouse B |
| 3 | مخزن C | Warehouse C |
| 4 | فان المندوب | Sales Van |

#### Example Requests

*All stores:*

GET /itemBalance?companyNumber=C001&salesmanCode=S012&itemNumber=231312


*Van only:*

GET /itemBalance?companyNumber=C001&salesmanCode=S012&itemNumber=231312&storeNo=4


#### Example Response — All Stores

