## Notes

- All *price fields* use 3 decimal places → "0.350"
- companyNumber and salesmanCode are required on *every request*
- itemBalance always returns an *array* even for a single store result
- Arabic text fields (*Ar) are always **UTF-8** encoded
- Date fields follow *DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm* format
- Image fields (itemPic, logo) return a full CDN URL or empty string ""